{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458920/extras/trap.gif?t=1739578224\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Winter 1845 - As the Wagon Leader you were supposed to get everyone to Oregon City already. But the air is getting colder and your party has run out of food and hope.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You find yourself in the back of your wagon, alone and starving. Losing grip on your sanity it's unclear how many moons have passed or how you are even still alive, but you must eat. As you commune with the spirit world in a last ditch effort to survive, you are offered a way out... if you play along.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458920/extras/plane.gif?t=1739578224\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Collect and craft cards as your party attempts to reach Oregon City </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Survive a series of increasingly difficult trail camp locations where you must build shelter and find food </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Manage temperature, hunger, sickness, repairs, and more </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Choose from 12 different 1-bit color palettes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458920/extras/vibecabin.gif?t=1739578224\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Launch Roadmap</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Forts on the trail where you can rest, trade, and repair</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Multiple maps to give the true scale of the Oregon Trail</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">River crossings</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Trail Calendar + Party must now eat on the Oregon Trail map</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Humans can equip cards that give bonuses (coat, gloves, amulet, etc)</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Entities that show up in the WAGON and offer you assistance</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">New occult tech tree</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Expand your cardgame playing area with portals to new Planes</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Improved shader</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Explorable starting area</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Revamped Encounter System</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">More cards / recipes</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Steam achievements / Cloud Save</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">More puzzles and secrets</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">More level biomes</span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <span class=\"bb_strike\">Last level</span></p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2458920?t=1739578224","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2458920?t=1739578224","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458920/9dbfda72b4674f101d00a0143bb4458dce785ba0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739578224","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i